; Derivation rules for the family-history example (spec §24).
; Declare and fire:  cave derive --db family.db examples/family-history/rules.cave
;
; Lines with `=>` are rules; everything else is prelude — vocabulary the
; conclusions need, ingested once.

GRANDPARENT-OF IS verb ; X is a grandparent of Y
GRANDPARENT-OF REVERSE GRANDCHILD-OF

?a PARENT-OF ?b, ?b PARENT-OF ?c => ?a GRANDPARENT-OF ?c ; two parent hops
